1. Unconstrained
2. Constrained (I think this is actually charge constrained)
3. IntegralConstrained 
- If you have an alternate proposel let me know.
- FunctionFitter is polymorphic so we have the recurring queston: Does the factory return a raw pointer, std:shared_ptr, std::unique_ptr or something else?
- The Fitting project-module needs more docs. Again use latex for formulas.

